","content":"Put a `<Button slot=\"trigger\">` and an `<InlineDrawerPanel>` inside `InlineDrawer`. The panel hides when collapsed and animates open."},"472":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-21","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#controlled","content":"Use `isExpanded` and `onExpandedChange` to drive state externally."},"473":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-22","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#sidebar-navigation","content":"A rail whose content stays visible when collapsed is a composition, not a mode: drive `isExpanded` yourself, render always-visible children (no `InlineDrawerPanel`), and let `minSize`/`maxSize` size the rail. Use numeric (px) sizes so the width animates; intrinsic keywords like `min-content`/`max-content` fit the content exactly but don't animate."},"474":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-23","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Key"},"475":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-24","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Action"},"476":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-25","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"`Enter` / `Space`"},"477":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-26","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Toggle via the slotted trigger"},"478":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-27","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"`Tab`"},"479":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-28","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"