Keys` and `onSelectionChange` for controlled state, or `defaultSelectedKeys` for uncontrolled."},"528":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-10","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#features","content":"**Layout primitive**: `ListBox` and `ListBoxItem` accept layout props (`gap`, `padding`, etc.) — they extend `FlexOwnProps`."},"529":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-11","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#features","content":"**Composes into other components**: `Select` uses `ListBox` internally; reach for `ListBox` directly when you need an inline list rather than a popover dropdown."},"530":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-12","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#features","content":"**React Aria integration**: Built on React Aria ListBox for accessibility, keyboard navigation, and typeahead."},"531":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-13","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#features","content":"`ListBox` requires either `aria-label` or `aria-labelledby`. For a labeled, popover-style picker, prefer `Select`."},"532":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-14","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#props","content":"The ListBox component accepts the following props:"},"533":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-15","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#basic","content":"Single selection with static children. Use `aria-label` to give the listbox an accessible name."},"534":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-16","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox#controlled","content":"Use `selectedKeys` and `onSelectionChange` for controlled state."},"535":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-17","page_id":"/docs/components/listbo